	<description><![CDATA[
	<p>One Web! is a responsive, 'mobile first' HTML5 template from <a href="http://internet-inspired.com">Internet Inspired!</a>.</p><p>It incorporates the hard work of others (proper coders, unlike me), I just rolled it all together and added some spit and polish to it. Notably, this template takes the HTML5 goodness and awesome polyfills from the <a href="http://html5boilerplate.com/">HTML5 Boilerplate</a> of Paul Irish, the mobile first logic and sexy typographic basics from <a href="http://www.stuffandnonsense.co.uk/projects/320andup/">320 and up</a> by Andy Clarke, some really neat Joomla! tricks and Google Font awesomeness from Matt Thomas' <a href="http://construct-framework.com/">Construct Framework</a> and a fluid <a href="http://cssgrid.net/">1140px Grid</a> grid from Andy Taylor.</p><p>What's left is the work of Seth Warburton @nternetinspired</p>
	]]></description>
		
